1
00:00:21,070 --> 00:00:24,180
笙ｪThe breeze of the 1990s drifts by笙ｪ

2
00:00:24,350 --> 00:00:27,180
笙ｪMemories slowly flicker past笙ｪ

3
00:00:27,650 --> 00:00:31,430
笙ｪMy heartbeat
rises and falls with the tune笙ｪ

4
00:00:31,500 --> 00:00:34,580
笙ｪThe story quietly begins here笙ｪ

5
00:00:35,330 --> 00:00:38,640
笙ｪUnder the dim lights, our eyes meet笙ｪ

6
00:00:38,710 --> 00:00:41,850
笙ｪTime seems to stand still笙ｪ

7
00:00:42,350 --> 00:00:45,990
笙ｪYour smile
breaks through the clouds like sun笙ｪ

8
00:00:46,060 --> 00:00:49,150
笙ｪMelting the snow deep in my heart笙ｪ

9
00:00:49,580 --> 00:00:53,090
笙ｪStreet posters spread signals of love笙ｪ

10
00:00:53,150 --> 00:00:56,110
笙ｪOur story slowly begins to ferment笙ｪ

11
00:00:56,800 --> 00:01:00,730
笙ｪHand in hand,
going through every dusk corner笙ｪ

12
00:01:00,930 --> 00:01:04,800
笙ｪThe taste of happiness is so subtle笙ｪ

13
00:01:05,480 --> 00:01:08,740
笙ｪCrossing back to the 1990s stage笙ｪ

14
00:01:09,150 --> 00:01:12,480
笙ｪYou're my most beautiful surprise笙ｪ

15
00:01:12,790 --> 00:01:16,210
笙ｪLove's flame burns within my heart笙ｪ

16
00:01:16,680 --> 00:01:19,710
笙ｪNot afraid of obstacles ahead笙ｪ

17
00:01:20,180 --> 00:01:23,560
笙ｪSway with the rhythm.
Feel your heart pound笙ｪ

18
00:01:23,660 --> 00:01:27,150
笙ｪThis love will never change笙ｪ

19
00:01:27,950 --> 00:01:35,080
笙ｪWe hold tight in this crazy era笙ｪ

20
00:01:35,160 --> 00:01:40,060
笙ｪ1990s love is what we rely on笙ｪ

21
00:01:40,100 --> 00:01:42,070
=Once More Love in 1995=

22
00:01:42,260 --> 00:01:44,937
=Episode 10=

23
00:01:47,159 --> 00:01:48,519
Mr. Qin.

24
00:01:50,079 --> 00:01:51,159
Mr. Qin.

25
00:01:52,650 --> 00:01:53,171
Mo.

26
00:01:53,262 --> 00:01:54,982
If you want to hit, hit me too.

27
00:01:55,519 --> 00:01:56,760
Zhou Zeyang, let me tell you.

28
00:01:57,159 --> 00:01:57,879
Starting today,

29
00:01:57,879 --> 00:01:58,879
you're out of Jinxin.

30
00:01:59,280 --> 00:02:01,040
Stay far away from Jiamin and Shanshan.

31
00:02:01,487 --> 00:02:02,567
Otherwise, if I see you,

32
00:02:02,959 --> 00:02:04,280
I'll make your life hell.

33
00:02:05,025 --> 00:02:05,784
Mr. Qin.

34
00:02:07,120 --> 00:02:08,439
This is all my fault.

35
00:02:09,080 --> 00:02:10,500
It has nothing to do with Jiamin.

36
00:02:10,960 --> 00:02:11,719
Mo,

37
00:02:11,960 --> 00:02:13,759
Zeyang and I truly love each other.

38
00:02:13,800 --> 00:02:15,400
He doesn't like Zhuang Shanshan.

39
00:02:16,800 --> 00:02:17,960
Truly love each other?

40
00:02:18,800 --> 00:02:19,810
Since you're so stubborn,

41
00:02:20,159 --> 00:02:21,919
get out of the Qin family
with Zhou Zeyang.

42
00:02:22,199 --> 00:02:23,280
Don't be my sister anymore.

43
00:02:23,479 --> 00:02:25,400
Mo. Zhuang Shanshan is a Zhuang.

44
00:02:25,400 --> 00:02:26,560
I'm the one surnamed Qin.

45
00:02:26,560 --> 00:02:28,000
Why should I leave the Qin family?

46
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:29,520
Because I run this household.

47
00:02:35,960 --> 00:02:36,599
Get out.

48
00:02:40,120 --> 00:02:41,319
Yan.

49
00:02:42,319 --> 00:02:43,039
Shanshan.

50
00:02:43,479 --> 00:02:44,280
Shanshan.

51
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:52,159
It's my fault for blowing things up.

52
00:02:53,599 --> 00:02:54,400
Shanshan.

53
00:02:56,199 --> 00:02:57,475
Since everyone's here today,

54
00:02:57,537 --> 00:02:58,056
I'll...

55
00:03:05,400 --> 00:03:07,120
Our troupe has disbanded.

56
00:03:12,960 --> 00:03:14,960
Don't talk too much.
Don't say what you shouldn't.

57
00:03:18,479 --> 00:03:20,680
Yan, what should I do?

58
00:03:20,680 --> 00:03:22,879
Does this mean I can never dance again?

59
00:03:22,960 --> 00:03:23,960
Impossible.

60
00:03:23,960 --> 00:03:26,400
There are so many troupes.
You can find another one later.

61
00:03:27,479 --> 00:03:28,039
Shanshan.

62
00:03:28,479 --> 00:03:29,560
Have some water first.

63
00:03:29,759 --> 00:03:30,960
What happened to your face?

64
00:03:32,600 --> 00:03:34,280
The company
had a sports meet this morning.

65
00:03:34,319 --> 00:03:36,199
Mr. Zhou took a hard fall.

66
00:03:36,919 --> 00:03:38,000
Does it still hurt?

67
00:03:39,080 --> 00:03:39,879
Jiamin.

68
00:03:41,400 --> 00:03:42,719
Go get my briefcase.

69
00:03:43,479 --> 00:03:44,680
I don't know where it is.

70
00:03:46,800 --> 00:03:47,520
Shanshan.

71
00:03:47,520 --> 00:03:48,000
Ah?

72
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:49,390
You don't need to worry about me.

73
00:03:49,800 --> 00:03:50,639
Zeyang.

74
00:03:50,960 --> 00:03:53,280
Did you come today especially for me?

75
00:03:57,000 --> 00:03:59,400
I didn't know your exact flight details.

76
00:03:59,919 --> 00:04:01,199
I was afraid you'd be upset,

77
00:04:01,199 --> 00:04:02,599
so I didn't dare ask too much.

78
00:04:03,479 --> 00:04:04,479
I just

79
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:06,240
waited for you here with Mr. Qin.

80
00:04:12,912 --> 00:04:13,631
Shanshan.

81
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:16,079
You've lost weight again recently.

82
00:04:16,199 --> 00:04:17,600
Have you not been eating properly?

83
00:04:18,680 --> 00:04:20,360
I don't have an appetite.

84
00:04:20,759 --> 00:04:21,920
That won't do.

85
00:04:22,120 --> 00:04:23,660
I'll make you a bowl of wonton noodles.

86
00:04:24,120 --> 00:04:24,920
Huh?

87
00:04:36,600 --> 00:04:37,560
Yan.

88
00:04:37,720 --> 00:04:38,160
Mm.

89
00:04:38,160 --> 00:04:39,480
Am I useless?

90
00:04:39,480 --> 00:04:40,520
I can't do anything right.

91
00:04:41,319 --> 00:04:42,399
Mom passed away early.

92
00:04:42,399 --> 00:04:44,079
Dad always protected me.

93
00:04:44,319 --> 00:04:45,759
Now, they're both gone.

94
00:04:46,199 --> 00:04:47,920
Luckily, I still have you and Qin.

95
00:04:48,000 --> 00:04:49,560
Zeyang doesn't mind me either.

96
00:04:53,199 --> 00:04:54,959
You're amazing.

97
00:04:55,680 --> 00:04:56,680
Your strengths

98
00:04:57,480 --> 00:04:59,319
are as many as your hair.

99
00:05:01,720 --> 00:05:02,959
You're kind.

100
00:05:03,959 --> 00:05:05,959
You're full of kindness toward everyone.

101
00:05:07,279 --> 00:05:08,519
You're resilient.

102
00:05:09,199 --> 00:05:11,319
No matter how hard it gets,
you can push through.

103
00:05:13,079 --> 00:05:14,519
And you're brave.

104
00:05:17,199 --> 00:05:18,480
Even without us,

105
00:05:18,600 --> 00:05:19,879
you can still live well.

106
00:05:21,600 --> 00:05:22,639
Yan.

107
00:05:22,959 --> 00:05:24,360
Are you really talking about me?

108
00:05:26,920 --> 00:05:27,920
Silly girl.

109
00:05:28,199 --> 00:05:29,759
(Mom relies on Zhou Zeyang so much.)

110
00:05:29,759 --> 00:05:31,160
(I have to find a way)

111
00:05:31,160 --> 00:05:33,160
(to dig him out of her heart.)

112
00:05:42,700 --> 00:05:44,960
You already foresaw what would happen
to the dance hall.

113
00:05:46,120 --> 00:05:46,920
So

114
00:05:47,839 --> 00:05:49,759
you sent me today to stop Zhou Zeyang.

115
00:05:50,720 --> 00:05:53,279
You were the one who swore
you could protect Shanshan.

116
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:58,839
(It seems I was overthinking.)

117
00:06:03,680 --> 00:06:05,319
I want to send Shanshan abroad to study.

118
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:07,600
She's already this heartbroken,

119
00:06:07,900 --> 00:06:09,959
and you want her to go alone
to a foreign country?

120
00:06:11,519 --> 00:06:13,800
Are you that eager
to make her make room for Qin Jiamin,

121
00:06:14,000 --> 00:06:16,399
so Zhou Zeyang and Qin Jiamin
can be together?

122
00:06:19,600 --> 00:06:20,439
Zhuang Yan.

123
00:06:20,959 --> 00:06:22,360
Jiamin is my birth sister.

124
00:06:22,380 --> 00:06:24,199
Shanshan has been
in this family for years.

125
00:06:24,199 --> 00:06:26,079
I've long treated her as family too.

126
00:06:26,519 --> 00:06:28,399
I can control everything about them,

127
00:06:28,480 --> 00:06:30,279
except their feelings.

128
00:06:34,560 --> 00:06:35,879
I know Shanshan too well.

129
00:06:37,560 --> 00:06:39,120
She should go out and see the world.

130
00:06:39,600 --> 00:06:40,959
See a bigger world

131
00:06:40,959 --> 00:06:42,279
and meet better people.

132
00:06:43,319 --> 00:06:45,560
Maybe then she can let go of Zhou Zeyang.

133
00:06:47,800 --> 00:06:49,560
What if she doesn't want to go?

134
00:06:49,820 --> 00:06:52,090
Are we supposed to tie her up
and send her onto the plane?

135
00:06:53,480 --> 00:06:55,319
That's why I'm discussing this with you.

136
00:06:55,800 --> 00:06:57,639
We have to send Shanshan abroad soon.

137
00:07:01,160 --> 00:07:01,800
Forget it.

138
00:07:05,600 --> 00:07:06,550
Get some rest early.

139
00:07:13,680 --> 00:07:14,560
(Qin Mo.)

140
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:16,680
(Even though this is unfair to you,)

141
00:07:17,160 --> 00:07:18,319
(I have no choice)

142
00:07:18,879 --> 00:07:19,959
(but do this for my mom.)

143
00:07:22,839 --> 00:07:23,519
Jiamin.

144
00:07:25,120 --> 00:07:25,759
Jiamin.

145
00:07:25,759 --> 00:07:26,759
Get away from me.

146
00:07:26,759 --> 00:07:28,360
Go cook wonton noodles
for Zhuang Shanshan.

147
00:07:28,360 --> 00:07:29,639
Go dote on her and please her.

148
00:07:29,639 --> 00:07:30,639
Go comfort her!

149
00:07:31,279 --> 00:07:32,519
Jiamin, listen to me.

150
00:07:32,519 --> 00:07:33,519
Listen to me.

151
00:07:33,639 --> 00:07:35,120
I was just acting.

152
00:07:35,720 --> 00:07:36,480
You saw it too.

153
00:07:36,480 --> 00:07:37,959
If I hadn't done that,

154
00:07:38,120 --> 00:07:39,862
would your brother and Zhuang Yan
let us go?

155
00:07:41,680 --> 00:07:43,439
I just took a beating,

156
00:07:43,839 --> 00:07:44,720
but what about you?

157
00:07:45,319 --> 00:07:47,439
You'd have to bear
the name of a homewrecker.

158
00:07:47,759 --> 00:07:49,360
How could I bear that?

159
00:07:51,120 --> 00:07:51,920
Jiamin.

160
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:54,120
Give me a bit more time, okay?

161
00:07:54,480 --> 00:07:56,079
Once I break up with Zhuang Shanshan,

162
00:07:56,560 --> 00:07:58,600
I'll be with you openly and properly .

163
00:07:59,439 --> 00:08:00,160
Really?

164
00:08:00,680 --> 00:08:01,839
I swear.

165
00:08:03,560 --> 00:08:04,800
Who wants you to swear?

166
00:08:05,600 --> 00:08:06,639
I trust you.

167
00:08:10,519 --> 00:08:11,680
After leaving the troupe,

168
00:08:11,680 --> 00:08:13,260
you revolve around Zhou Zeyang all day.

169
00:08:13,879 --> 00:08:16,600
Is becoming a man's accessory
your dream?

170
00:08:17,279 --> 00:08:18,399
But I think

171
00:08:18,560 --> 00:08:20,560
supporting my husband and raising kids
isn't bad.

172
00:08:20,959 --> 00:08:22,959
Even though I don't have a job now,

173
00:08:22,959 --> 00:08:23,680
I can still

174
00:08:23,680 --> 00:08:25,920
build a warm home with Zeyang.

175
00:08:32,840 --> 00:08:33,639
Ah.

176
00:08:34,440 --> 00:08:35,080
Not mad anymore?

177
00:08:35,080 --> 00:08:36,399
Yan, what are you doing?

178
00:08:36,600 --> 00:08:38,519
I think you make sense.

179
00:08:38,879 --> 00:08:40,360
I spoke without thinking.

180
00:08:40,360 --> 00:08:41,360
I apologize to you.

181
00:08:41,960 --> 00:08:44,600
Yan, I wasn't angry at all.

182
00:08:51,480 --> 00:08:53,159
Your temper is just too good.

183
00:08:53,159 --> 00:08:54,350
That puts me in a tough spot.

184
00:08:55,679 --> 00:08:56,120
Oh.

185
00:08:56,120 --> 00:08:56,960
It's almost six.

186
00:08:56,960 --> 00:08:58,120
Yan, I'll stop talking.

187
00:08:58,120 --> 00:08:59,630
I'm going to see Zeyang at the company.

188
00:09:00,762 --> 00:09:01,402
Shanshan.

189
00:09:02,600 --> 00:09:05,360
Zhou Zeyang is so busy with work.

190
00:09:05,480 --> 00:09:07,440
You barely see him each month.

191
00:09:08,360 --> 00:09:10,120
Do you want to be with him every day?

192
00:09:17,087 --> 00:09:19,500
(Jinxin)

193
00:09:20,679 --> 00:09:21,240
Shanshan.

194
00:09:21,639 --> 00:09:22,399
Why are you here?

195
00:09:22,960 --> 00:09:25,559
Qin, I want to discuss something.

196
00:09:26,159 --> 00:09:27,200
The troupe disbanded.

197
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:29,320
Staying home is too boring.

198
00:09:29,480 --> 00:09:30,137
I...

199
00:09:30,600 --> 00:09:32,600
I want to work at Jinxin
and gain some experience.

200
00:09:35,810 --> 00:09:36,799
Is this your idea or...

201
00:09:36,799 --> 00:09:37,840
It's my idea.

202
00:09:41,480 --> 00:09:43,759
If it's inconvenient, forget it.

203
00:09:43,759 --> 00:09:44,879
Qin, get back to work.

204
00:09:44,879 --> 00:09:45,759
I won't disturb you.

205
00:09:45,759 --> 00:09:46,720
I didn't say no.

206
00:09:47,919 --> 00:09:48,519
Shanshan.

207
00:09:48,960 --> 00:09:50,720
It's a good thing you want to join.

208
00:09:50,860 --> 00:09:52,159
You can learn the business early.

209
00:09:52,360 --> 00:09:54,759
I can also transfer the shares
your dad left you earlier.

210
00:09:55,320 --> 00:09:56,960
That's not what I meant, Qin.

211
00:09:57,480 --> 00:09:59,712
Jinxin is thriving
under your management.

212
00:09:59,919 --> 00:10:01,639
If it were me,

213
00:10:01,679 --> 00:10:02,875
it'd be a total mess.

214
00:10:03,159 --> 00:10:04,879
It's fine, take it slow.

215
00:10:05,159 --> 00:10:06,600
I can teach you what you don't know.

216
00:10:08,519 --> 00:10:09,960
Oh, by the way,

217
00:10:10,559 --> 00:10:11,919
go call Zhuang Yan for me.

218
00:10:11,919 --> 00:10:13,120
I have instructions for her.

219
00:10:13,200 --> 00:10:13,960
Okay.

220
00:10:21,159 --> 00:10:23,559
Why do you need me?

221
00:10:24,279 --> 00:10:25,080
Zhuang Yan.

222
00:10:26,639 --> 00:10:28,679
Letting Shanshan join
was your idea, right?

223
00:10:28,879 --> 00:10:30,799
Didn't we agree she'd study abroad?

224
00:10:31,080 --> 00:10:31,919
What are you doing?

225
00:10:33,120 --> 00:10:34,799
It's for her own good, right?

226
00:10:35,799 --> 00:10:37,840
Are you afraid that once she joins,

227
00:10:38,080 --> 00:10:40,840
she'll disrupt Zhou Zeyang
and Qin Jiamin's relationship?

228
00:10:41,759 --> 00:10:42,720
Or is it that

229
00:10:42,720 --> 00:10:45,279
you're worried
she'll fight you for power

230
00:10:45,279 --> 00:10:46,480
and shake your authority?

231
00:10:48,320 --> 00:10:49,360
As long as I'm here,

232
00:10:49,520 --> 00:10:50,600
don't even think about it.

233
00:11:07,919 --> 00:11:10,519
Why put it there blocking my view?
Take it out.

234
00:11:11,159 --> 00:11:13,480
Boss, isn't this the mirror you wanted?

235
00:11:15,262 --> 00:11:16,062
I'll move it now.

236
00:11:21,360 --> 00:11:23,080
This is the office area.

237
00:11:24,120 --> 00:11:26,360
My desk used to be right here.

238
00:11:26,360 --> 00:11:27,159
The view here...

239
00:11:27,159 --> 00:11:28,159
Sorry.

240
00:11:30,600 --> 00:11:31,440
Qin Jiamin?

241
00:11:31,500 --> 00:11:32,280
Forget I said that.

242
00:11:32,400 --> 00:11:33,720
Come on, I'll take you upstairs.

243
00:11:34,725 --> 00:11:35,864
Why did you bring her here?

244
00:11:36,559 --> 00:11:40,240
Starting today,
Shanshan officially joins Jinxin.

245
00:11:40,360 --> 00:11:42,440
She'll be a sales executive under me.

246
00:11:43,039 --> 00:11:43,879
Her?

247
00:11:44,125 --> 00:11:45,660
Has she studied sales for even one day?

248
00:11:46,039 --> 00:11:48,350
Can the Zhuang family be more realistic?

249
00:11:48,559 --> 00:11:49,440
Zhuang Shanshan.

250
00:11:49,440 --> 00:11:51,240
If you know what's good for you,
leave now.

251
00:11:51,300 --> 00:11:53,470
If you mess things up,
no one will clean up after you.

252
00:11:54,320 --> 00:11:56,080
Maybe we should forget it, Yan.

253
00:11:56,679 --> 00:11:57,799
With me here,

254
00:11:58,159 --> 00:11:59,360
no one can drive you away.

255
00:12:01,837 --> 00:12:02,437
Don't worry.

256
00:12:02,799 --> 00:12:04,159
Stick with me and learn slowly.

257
00:12:04,519 --> 00:12:05,679
With your ability,

258
00:12:05,919 --> 00:12:06,639
in three months,

259
00:12:07,000 --> 00:12:08,879
I'll show everyone how capable you are.

260
00:12:11,679 --> 00:12:12,480
Let's go.

261
00:12:15,537 --> 00:12:17,950
(Jinxin Food Co. Ltd)

262
00:12:27,237 --> 00:12:29,087
笙ｪYou dodge the question笙ｪ

263
00:12:29,137 --> 00:12:32,750
笙ｪThe revolving door
spins out a heartbeat笙ｪ

264
00:12:32,850 --> 00:12:36,837
笙ｪLeopard print dress
steps on neon rhymes笙ｪ

265
00:12:36,837 --> 00:12:40,362
笙ｪThe jukebox swallows our coins笙ｪ

266
00:12:40,412 --> 00:12:44,575
笙ｪCue Love Like the Tide as our signal笙ｪ

267
00:12:44,887 --> 00:12:48,437
笙ｪFrom the disco ball's shattered light笙ｪ

268
00:12:48,575 --> 00:12:55,462
笙ｪI fall into your arms,
learning a naughty dance笙ｪ

269
00:13:00,039 --> 00:13:01,440
This is the proposal you made?

270
00:13:01,440 --> 00:13:02,720
If we give this to the client,

271
00:13:02,720 --> 00:13:04,799
Jinxin's reputation
will go down the drain.

272
00:13:04,960 --> 00:13:05,879
I'll fix it right now.

273
00:13:06,480 --> 00:13:07,080
Fix it?

274
00:13:07,080 --> 00:13:08,162
Do you even have the skills?

275
00:13:08,350 --> 00:13:10,519
All you do is hide behind
my brother and Zhuang Yan.

276
00:13:10,919 --> 00:13:11,759
Loser.

277
00:13:13,000 --> 00:13:13,519
Qin Jiamin.

278
00:13:13,519 --> 00:13:14,680
What nonsense are you saying?

279
00:13:15,759 --> 00:13:17,760
Touch my people again,
and I won't go easy on you.

280
00:13:20,679 --> 00:13:21,480
Let's go.

281
00:13:22,759 --> 00:13:23,559
Ah.

282
00:13:25,559 --> 00:13:26,480
Yan.

283
00:13:27,000 --> 00:13:28,639
Did I let you down?

284
00:13:28,919 --> 00:13:30,519
Don't be silly.

285
00:13:30,639 --> 00:13:32,679
In my eyes, you're always the best.

286
00:13:34,000 --> 00:13:35,120
It's all Qin Jiamin's fault,

287
00:13:35,120 --> 00:13:36,390
stirring up trouble for nothing.

288
00:13:36,600 --> 00:13:38,480
Don't give up on yourself
because of her.

289
00:13:38,480 --> 00:13:39,759
I won't give up.

290
00:13:40,000 --> 00:13:41,559
You've done so much for me.

291
00:13:41,559 --> 00:13:42,559
I'll work harder.

292
00:13:42,559 --> 00:13:43,360
Mm.

293
00:13:47,159 --> 00:13:49,000
Zhuang Yan's crazy.

294
00:13:49,000 --> 00:13:49,720
How rude.

295
00:13:57,512 --> 00:13:58,071
Zeyang.

296
00:13:58,720 --> 00:13:59,080
You...

297
00:13:59,360 --> 00:14:00,600
What are you doing?

298
00:14:18,750 --> 00:14:22,388
笙ｪThe old dial tone circles in my ear笙ｪ

299
00:14:22,513 --> 00:14:25,825
笙ｪFaded tickets point to a cicada summer笙ｪ

300
00:14:25,988 --> 00:14:29,575
笙ｪThe videotape
whispers your image in the frame笙ｪ

301
00:14:29,875 --> 00:14:33,163
笙ｪAgainst the light, the plaid shirt
reveals a clear and transparent smile笙ｪ

302
00:14:33,388 --> 00:14:37,013
笙ｪI'm a clumsy guest in a frozen scene笙ｪ

303
00:14:37,175 --> 00:14:40,513
笙ｪHow do I answer familiar lines?笙ｪ

304
00:14:40,588 --> 00:14:44,300
笙ｪI know
the train will leave this station笙ｪ

305
00:14:44,350 --> 00:14:48,213
笙ｪI know the ending's in a faded future笙ｪ

306
00:14:48,275 --> 00:14:54,325
笙ｪYet I want to approach that warmth笙ｪ

307
00:14:55,500 --> 00:15:02,238
笙ｪEven one second rewrites missed lines笙ｪ

308
00:15:02,525 --> 00:15:06,800
笙ｪRewind to 1995,
back to the street we met笙ｪ

309
00:15:06,800 --> 00:15:10,100
笙ｪWind blows through the sycamore leaves
and lands on your shoulder笙ｪ

310
00:15:10,175 --> 00:15:14,475
笙ｪI wish I could pause and stop time笙ｪ

311
00:15:14,538 --> 00:15:18,188
笙ｪLet unspoken love
be preserved forever as amber笙ｪ

312
00:15:18,188 --> 00:15:21,750
笙ｪRewind to 1995,
gentle touch of fingertips笙ｪ

313
00:15:21,800 --> 00:15:25,063
笙ｪStar sparks in your eyes burn my chest笙ｪ

314
00:15:25,063 --> 00:15:28,813
笙ｪThis looping script
is beyond my saving笙ｪ

315
00:15:28,813 --> 00:15:35,525
笙ｪI can only stay with you till the end
in this inverted hourglass笙ｪ
